attributionInfo.brokerName: Keller Williams Realty Boston-Metro | Back Bay

description: Dockside Place - Move right in to this stunning TOP FLOOR  845 sq ft  brick and beam loft  located in the heart of the Seaport with dramatic city skyline and water views. Brand new renovation- features include appx 12 ft ceiling height, beautiful kitchen with white cabinetry, quartz counters, SS appliances, a spa like bath & dressing room with classic black and white tile and new fixtures. An expansive floor plan with grand proportions allows for easy partitioning of a living/dining and separate sleeping areas. Painted throughout in soft fresh colors and accent walls, there is brand new flooring, new windows, new custom lighting fixtures, 5 generous closets and a full size in unit washer & dryer. Located in the one of the most popular neighborhoods in the city, convenient to a multitude of restaurants, shops, entertainment venues and green space, with easy access to major commuter routes ,T, South Station & airport. Nice option for a first time buyer, pied a terre or investor rental.
